songs.lyrics:
[Interlude: Hi-Tek]
Yeah, yeah, what up tho. It’s ya boy Hi-Tek. I’m representin’ right now with my boy Kweli. It’s the The Beautiful Mixtape Vol. 2, you know what I’m sayin’, The Struggle Continues Mothafuckas! Let’s get this shit goin’ baby
